## General Info
This project is focused on visualizing the safety of airline travel.
Several different data sources and visualization tools are utilized for this project.
The primary file for this project is the presentation of data and visualizations.

## Data
The data for this project was obtained from the sources below:
https://www.airlines.org/dataset/world-airlines-traffic-and-capacity/#
https://github.com/fivethirtyeight/data/tree/master/airline-safety
https://data.world/data-society/airplane-crashes
https://www.statista.com/statistics/263443/worldwide-air-traffic-fatalities/
https://www.bts.gov/content/transportation-fatalities-mode

## Setup
To run this project:
1. run the presentation included in the repository
